<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ema612_02_IH_0001</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema612_02.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema612_02_ih_0001 paging">
      <section class="title type2 score">
        <h2 data-head="1_green" lang="y">도형을 보고 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">두 면이 평행하고 합동인 다각형으로 이루어진 입체도형을 모두 고르세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA612_02_IH/0001_01.png" alt="" />
              <p class="text1">가</p>
              <p class="text2">나</p>
              <p class="text3">다</p>
              <p class="text4">라</p>
              <p class="text5">마</p>
              <div class="boolean_wrap">
                <button class="button1" type="button" data-answer-single="true"></button>
                <button class="button2" type="button" data-answer-single="true"></button>
                <button class="button3" type="button" data-answer-single="false"></button>
                <button class="button4" type="button" data-answer-single="true"></button>
                <button class="button5" type="button" data-answer-single="false"></button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 해설 -->
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">두 면이 평행하고 합동인 다각형으로 이루어진 입체도형을 찾으면 가,나,라입니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="btn_area">
            <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">두 면이 평행하고 합동인 다각형으로 이루어진 입체도형을 모두 고르세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA612_02_IH/0001_01.png" alt="" />
              <p class="text1">가</p>
              <p class="text2">나</p>
              <p class="text3">다</p>
              <p class="text4">라</p>
              <p class="text5">마</p>
            </div>
            <div class="input_wrap mt_30">
              <math-field data-answer-single="각기둥" text-align="center" class="large"></math-field>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 해설 -->
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">두 면이 평행하고 합동인 다각형으로 이루어진 입체도형을 각기둥이라고 합니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="btn_area">
            <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
